      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a museum-grade 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo, retaining its original 2JZ-GTE power plant and Getrag V160 6-speed manual transmission. This MKIV features the factory sequential twin-turbocharger configuration, delivering a linear power band with zero boost leaks. The chassis remains structurally flawless, complemented by a factory Torsen limited-slip differential. Meticulously maintained with documented compression numbers across all six cylinders and original VIN tags on all panels. The suspension geometry is factory-spec, and the undercarriage is free of oxidation. A true collector-grade example for the discerning purist.",
