      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade masterpiece that redefines the standard for pre-owned excellence. This vehicle is in pristine, showroom condition, having been meticulously garaged and climate-controlled since day one. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster with absolutely zero rock chips, swirl marks, or imperfections across the bodywork. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of luxury; the premium leather seats show no signs of bolster wear, and the original factory scent still lingers. Every button, dial, and electronic feature operates with the crisp precision of a brand-new car. Mechanically, the vehicle is beyond reproach, boasting a documented service history with all maintenance performed exclusively by certified technicians. Underneath, the chassis is as clean as the body, reflecting a life of fair-weather driving only. Included are all original keys, owner\u2019s manuals, and the original window sticker. This is not just a car; it is a time capsule for the discerning enthusiast who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
